      <exercise>
        <webwork seed="1">
          <setup>
            <var name="$ans">
              <static>1.1</static>
            </var>
            <pg-code>
              $ans=1.1;
            </pg-code>
          </setup>
          <statement>
            <p>Given that <m>e^0=1</m>, approximate the value of <m>e^{0.1}</m> using the tangent line to <m>f(x) = e^x</m> at <m>x=0</m>.</p>
            <p><var name = "$ans" width="5" /></p>
          </statement>
          <solution>
            <p>The tangent line to <m>f(x) = e^x</m> at <m>x=0</m> is <m>y=x+1</m>; thus <m>e^{0.1} \approx y(0.1) = 1.1</m>.</p>
          </solution>
        </webwork>
      </exercise>

